'-------------------------------------------------------------- 
'This file describes how to do a parametric Rietveld fit to PXRD patterns of WO3 collected on cooling from
'room temperature to 90 K as the sample changes from the P21/n phase to the P-1 phase and then to the Pc phase.
'Its use is described in the tutorial https://topas.webspace.durham.ac.uk/tutorial-surface-3/
'
'November 2020
'file developed from wo3_t0000_04.inp from the surface_new tutorial and gave Rwp 12.649%
'Set up with #list, for xdds and strs in a format for surface fitting for topas v8 onwards with .sv output
'With TCHz included gives identical 12.469% to parametric_04.inp for 188 parameters (11 data sets)
'With TCHz excluded much faster and 12.873% for 184 parameters (11 data sets)
'Rwp 12.874% in topas v8 2/10/2023 for  11 data sets  184 parameters
'Rwp 12.805% in topas v8 2/10/2023 for 100 data sets 1163 parameters
'
'21/5/2024 switched to using an fn function for cell parameters
'Rwp 12.873% in topas v8 21/5/2024 for  11 data sets  184 parameters with convolution step 2
'Rwp 12.807% in topas v8 2/10/2023 for 100 data sets 1163 parameters 100 iters in 651 seconds
'-------------------------------------------------------------- 
 
r_wp  12.8073436 r_exp  8.94673 r_p  9.93074443 r_wp_dash  18.9317847 r_p_dash  16.4142711 r_exp_dash  13.225035 weighted_Durbin_Watson  100.739622 gof  1.43151113
 
'{{{ 1. Refinement choices, iters, output, backup, etc 
iters 200 
chi2_convergence_criteria 0.001 
continue_after_convergence 
'do_errors 
no_LIMIT_warnings 
load_save_locals 
out_refinement_stats
'#define riet_out 'to write various files to separate folders 
#define write_out  'write results file 
#define param_cell 'use this to parametrically fit cell parameter 
 
'create backup in first cycle and remove old results.txt file
#if (Run_Number == 0) 
 Backup_INP 
 system_before_save_OUT  { del results.txt } 
 out "results.txt" append  
 Out_String("   Temp(K)      Rwp(%)     Perc_P21n    Esd      Scale_P21n  Esd            a_P21n      Esd         b_P21n      Esd         c_P21n      Esd        alpha_P21n   ESD        beta_P21n    Esd        gamma_P21n   Esd       Vol_P21n      Esd        Perc_Pb1     Esd      Scale_Pb1   Esd            a_Pb1       Esd         b_Pb1       Esd         c_Pb1       Esd        alpha_Pb1    ESD        beta_Pb1     Esd        gamma_Pb1    Esd       Vol_Pb1       Esd        Perc_Pc      Esd      Scale_Pc    Esd            a_Pc        Esd         b_Pc        Esd         c_Pc        Esd        alpha_Pc     ESD        beta_Pc      Esd        gamma_Pc     Esd       Vol_Pc        Esd")  
#endif 
'}}} 
 
